Susan Sobbott 

		
		President, Global Commercial Payments, 

	
		 American Express Company 	

 
Last Updated: 04/20/2017 



Executive Summary
An American Express veteran, Susan Sobbott joined the organization back in 1989. She serves as President of Global Commercial Payments. Most recently, she was President of Global Corporate Payments of the company, where she was responsible for the products that serve American Express’ corporate payment clients around the world, i 
Personal Attributes and Interests

She has two children, Leah and Jeremiah, with her husband, Keith. They live in New Jersey.
She enjoys spending time with her family and restoring her home. 
