Ms. Susan Sobbott serves as the President of Global Corporate Payments, a multi-billion dollar global division of the American Express Company serving the payment needs of mid-sized and large companies. Ms. Sobbott has been President of Global Payments of American Express Company. since January 2014. From 2004 to early 2014, she was President and General Manager of American Express OPEN, a multi-billion dollar business unit within American Express Company. Since 2009, Ms. Sobbott has also served as a member of the Business Operating Committee, a group of senior leaders at American Express Company working with the Chief Executive Officer to develop strategic direction. She serves as Director of The Children’s Place Retail Stores, Inc. Ms. Sobbott has held various executive positions of increasing responsibility since joining American Express Company in 1990. Ms. Sobbott has leadership experience in developing and executing business strategies in such areas as new product innovation, business development, customer service and relationship management.



